                "invention-title": "Energy-source system"
            },
            "abstract": {
                "p": "There is an energy system, which includes the solar heating device, oxyhydrogen fuel forming device, burning heating device, steam forming device and steam generator. The function of the solar heating device can heat the water passing through it, the preheating water can be supplied to the steam forming device, and then which is electrolyzed into the oxygen and hydrogen in the oxyhydrogen fuel forming device, and these can be as fuel of the burning heating device, which takes advantage of the fuel to heat the hot water again in the steam forming device. The steam forming device can storage the preheated water from the solar heating device and makes them changed to steam. So the steam generator can make use of the steam to generate the electricity, output the electricity to the load device and oxyhydrogen fuel forming device. This invention takes advantage of the solar energy, hydrogen and oxygen to heat the hot water, and the produce the steam to drive the steam generator producing the electricity."
